> specifying:
> 
> - name/surname
> - affiliation
> - short bio
> - email address
> - title
> - abstract
> 
> Deadline for submitting topics/presentations is December 9, 2024.
> Notifications for accepted topics/presentations will be sent out
> December 16, 2024.
